---

## ğŸ”¤ Markdown Syntax Explained

| Syntax | Meaning | Example |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `#` | H1 (main heading) | `# Project Title` |
| `##` | H2 (sub-heading) | `## Features` |
| `**text**` | Bold | `**Important**` |
| `*text*` | Italic | `*Optional*` |
| `` `code` `` | Inline code | `` `python3 app.py` `` |
| \`\`\`python | Code block | ```python<br>print("Hello")<br>``` |
| `-` or `*` | Bullet list | `- Item` |
| `[text](url)` | Link | `[GitHub](https://github.com)` |
| `![alt](img.png)` | Image | `![Logo](logo.png)` |

---

